PSA: 2025 WPILib requires 2025 vendor dependencies Programming
Since we get piles of questions about this every year, posting this PSA again. 2025.1.1 WPILib requires 2025 vendor dep builds. 2024 vendor deps will not work. Nor will vendor deps from the 2025 beta. All vendor deps must be rebuilt against the release build before they will work.
